snippet.title: Pathfinder Wrath of the Righteous Nintendo Switch (cloud) GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
Hey there, fellow adventurers! Grab your swords, spellbooks, and Switches, because we're diving into the epic world of Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous (CLOUD VERSION)

Sound coming from the Switch was captured via audio recorder - ZOOM H1. Video captured with Panasonic GX80 in 4k.
